data.description: This sprawling, well maintained 5 bedrooms, 3 full bathroom home in the popular Highway H Development is only minutes from the west gate of Fort Leonard Wood! This home has a lot to offer with recessed lighting, octagon ceilings and full finished walk out basement! Enter into the home through the expansive living room, featuring beautiful laminate flooring and an abundance of natural lighting. The oversized kitchen with combination dining area features custom cabinetry and plenty of counter space for all your culinary gadgets. The owner's suite has plenty of room for a large bedroom set and an en suite bathroom with a massive jetted tub, perfect for relaxing after a long day. Just across the hall is one roomy spare bedroom. Head downstairs and find 3 more bedrooms, spacious family room, gas fireplace and a full bathroom. Whatever you do, don't miss out on this home! Call your agent today to schedule your private viewing! Square footage and dimensions are approximate.
